<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kei ka chenna zie lei mun hi,
 Gamgaw, gamthip lungngaih na mai;
 Zielam a khun awl leh chieh ka,
 Belam No Lal Isu kawm ah;
 Kei ka chenna ding gamnom khu,
 Ka ngai ie khensate lenna;
 En zel ing ka, tatsate nawp-
 Lenna gam nuom chu.

[V2]
 Ka tup gam nuom ka chenna ding,
 Leiah gimtheih thuok mahleng le;
 Ei Hukdampa'n gimtheite di'n,
 Hinna tuikhuk pha a luonsak.

[V3]
 2. Aw ei Tanpa Na thawkna chu,
 Nei hehpihnan ngai thei leu hing;
 Bangkim a ka bangkim na hi,
 Ka thagau din bangkim na hi,
 Sana khawpi nuoma leng di'n,
 Na thawkna hin a chawzo hi,
 Aw nei khawtuohna a hi ie,
 Kei migilo hi.

[V4]
 3. Aw Lal Isu mu thei leng chu,
 Lungdeihte tuola lennau chu;
 Kalvari hehpihna ziekin,
 Chitin, namtin te a leng ui;
 Keile Na thawkgim na zalin,
 Gamgaw gamthip hun pawtsan ka;
 Hehpihna Lalpa ei puiin,
 Lungsietna gamah.

[V5]
 4. Khawvel lopi leh hawihna hi,
 Beizel ina, a hawihna tawh;
 Hukdampa kawm ah leng ingka,
 A lopina gam vak hawih ah;
 Leisiet kipahna ngai puong ka,
 Chun A hehpihna chunga chun;
 Kumsawt kipahna la sai tiu;
 Belam No kawm ah.</lyrics>
<title>Belam No Vang Khuo</title>
<hymn_number>183</hymn_number>
</song>